<p><b>Jonathan B. Spira</b> (born 1961) is a <a href="/wiki/Researcher" title="Researcher" class="mw-redirect">researcher</a> and <a href="/wiki/Industry_analyst" title="Industry analyst">industry analyst</a> known for his work in the area of collaboration and knowledge sharing and the problem of <a href="/wiki/Information_overload" title="Information overload">information overload</a>.</p>
<p></p>
